Properties.Description:
QuA meat quality grade placed on each carcass by the U.S. Department of Agriculture inspector at the packing plant. 

Quality grade is based on the degree of marbling and degree of maturity. Color, texture and firmness of lean also are used in the final quality grade determination.

Ex:
- Prime
- Choice
- Select
- Standard
- Commercial
- Cutter
-  Canner
